These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, skateboarding, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##8
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |    3     |
| Sport   | volleyball | skateboarding | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, rock-climbing, filmmaking
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3     |
| Hobby   | card-games | filmmaking | rock-climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, almond-milk, mirinda
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking coffee is not to the right of the person drinking mirinda##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |  3  |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | coffee | mirinda |

 #################################

 
