.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-5::.
There are 3 different nationalities: mexican, argentine, russian
1. the argentine is in an even position##4
2. the argentine is not to the right of the russian##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3     |
| Nationality   | mexican | argentine | russian |

